  'Compare ionic radii: why cations shrink, anions swell, and isoelectronic series order by nuclear charge',
  'Explain first and successive ionization energies, the core-electron jump, and the group 2 to 13 and 15 to 16 dips',
  'Define electron affinity and electronegativity and identify the most electronegative elements',
  'Relate metallic character and reactivity trends to Z_eff and ionization energy',
  'Characterize the alkali metals, alkaline earths, halogens, noble gases, and transition metals',
